He has posted pictures of himself as an aviator, discussed golf on social media, and has been involved in youth empowerment issues. He has strong views about gangsterism in prisons and the development of township economies.  Now he has emerged as the leader of a campaign against foreign nationals living in South Africa. These are the many faces of Nhlanhla Lux Dlamini, known as Nhlanhla Lux, the leader of #OperationDudula. Since its first online appearance in June 2021, #OperationDudula has become one of the most popular hashtags calling for the removal of illegal foreign nationals in South Africa, alongside #PutSouthAfricaFirst. #OperationDudula has expanded beyond an online conversation and now operates as a vigilante group that targets foreign nationals and their businesses. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1232269" src="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-1.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="400" srcset="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-1.jpg 1801w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-1.jpg?resize=480,267 480w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-1.jpg?resize=768,426 768w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-1.jpg?resize=720,400 720w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-1.jpg?resize=1536,853 1536w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-1.jpg?resize=1280,711 1280w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-1.jpg?resize=1600,888 1600w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-1.jpg?resize=350,194 350w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /> As fears of an escalation of social tensions and violence grow in many communities, the Centre for Analytics and Behavioural Change (CABC) looked at some of the factors that drive the online conversation around #OperationDudula. The first of these factors is the account of the group’s leader: @nhlanhla_lux_ . A timeline analysis reveals that since its creation in June 2014, the account shared a number of low traction posts, predominantly with Instagram links that were either broken or unfollowed. This trend continued until 2018, when the posts began to gain some traction. Many of these posts were about golf and aviation, specifically Native Airways, which Lux claimed to own. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1232270" src="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-2.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="400" srcset="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-2.jpg 1801w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-2.jpg?resize=480,267 480w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-2.jpg?resize=768,426 768w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-2.jpg?resize=720,400 720w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-2.jpg?resize=1536,853 1536w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-2.jpg?resize=1280,711 1280w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-2.jpg?resize=1600,888 1600w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-2.jpg?resize=350,194 350w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /> At this time, the account also engaged in conversation around social issues such as gangsterism in prisons and the development of township economies. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1232271" src="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-3.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="400" srcset="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-3.jpg 1801w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-3.jpg?resize=480,267 480w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-3.jpg?resize=768,426 768w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-3.jpg?resize=720,400 720w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-3.jpg?resize=1536,853 1536w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-3.jpg?resize=1280,711 1280w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-3.jpg?resize=1600,888 1600w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-3.jpg?resize=350,194 350w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /> In July 2021 Lux was involved in protecting Maponya Mall from looters during the unrest. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1232272" src="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-4.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="400" srcset="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-4.jpg 1801w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-4.jpg?resize=480,267 480w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-4.jpg?resize=768,426 768w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-4.jpg?resize=720,400 720w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-4.jpg?resize=1536,853 1536w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-4.jpg?resize=1280,711 1280w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-4.jpg?resize=1600,888 1600w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-4.jpg?resize=350,194 350w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" />The account’s focus on developing township economies and driving the “Soweto spaza business accountability program”, which ensured that spaza shops supported local entrepreneurs, continued in August 2021. The theme of “patriotic citizenship” was then introduced in the account’s posts. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1232273" src="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-5.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="400" srcset="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-5.jpg 1801w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-5.jpg?resize=480,267 480w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-5.jpg?resize=768,426 768w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-5.jpg?resize=720,400 720w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-5.jpg?resize=1536,853 1536w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-5.jpg?resize=1280,711 1280w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-5.jpg?resize=1600,888 1600w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-5.jpg?resize=350,194 350w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" />In October, the account engaged in conversation related to the local government elections. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1232274" src="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-6.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="400" srcset="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/upload