inalCABCfacesoflux-inset-12.png?resize=768,198 768w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-12.png?resize=720,186 720w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-12.png?resize=1280,330 1280w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-12.png?resize=350,90 350w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" />The CABC also found that while Lux leads the physical mobilisation of #OperationDudula and receives high traction on posts around the operation, he is not included in the top 10 authors within the conversation. Among the top authors is the @Lolobee93658919 account, which accounts for 3,624 mentions between 1 June 2021 and 6 April 2022. With more than 30,000 tweets since its creation in February this year, the @Lolobee93658919 account has been posting content predominantly linked to #PutSouthafricaFirst and #OperationDudula. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1232286" src="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-14.png" alt="" width="720" height="400" srcset="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-14.png 1345w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-14.png?resize=480,267 480w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-14.png?resize=768,427 768w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-14.png?resize=720,400 720w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-14.png?resize=1280,711 1280w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-14.png?resize=350,194 350w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" />An analysis of the account’s last 2,195 tweets shows that 84% of @Lolobee93658919 content are retweets, not original content. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1232287" src="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-15.png" alt="" width="720" height="296" srcset="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-15.png 1412w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-15.png?resize=480,197 480w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-15.png?resize=768,315 768w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-15.png?resize=720,296 720w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-15.png?resize=1280,526 1280w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-15.png?resize=350,144 350w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" />This account has also been flagged for its high tweet frequency, which averages 491 a day since the account’s creation and 549 a day for the last 2,195 tweets. <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1232288" src="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-16.png" alt="" width="720" height="387" srcset="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-16.png 1427w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-16.png?resize=480,258 480w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-16.png?resize=768,413 768w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-16.png?resize=720,387 720w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-16.png?resize=1280,689 1280w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/finalCABCfacesoflux-inset-16.png?resize=350,188 350w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /> The secon